body:
In my last League of Legends game I ran into a fairly concerning issue (not sure what caused it) that is making my game crash. I do not get bugsplat reports, it simply puts the "Attempting to Reconnect" bar on my screen and freezes me there. I had to manually exit the game and then reconnect twice in one match. I was able to reconnect no problem, but could not nail down what was making me crash. It is not my internet connection; I was able to run youtube music and a discord application in the background. This appears to be something to do with riot servers, so anything you can do would be greatly appreciated! 

Any others who have had this issue RECENTLY, please comment below so the RIOT staff can get us all in one swoop. :)

Your friendly sweaty scientist, {{item:3071}} {{champion:36}} {{item:3071}}
